sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(via ModelMesh Service)
    participant Proxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Marshaler as Custom JSON<br/>Marshaler
    participant GRPC as ModelMesh gRPC Server<br/>8033/TCP gRPC

    Note over Client,GRPC: Flow 1: REST-to-gRPC Inference Request

    Client->>Proxy: POST /v2/models/{model_name}/infer<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS
    Proxy->>Marshaler: Decode JSON request body<br/>In-process
    Marshaler-->>Proxy: Protobuf ModelInferRequest<br/>(tensor data unmarshaled)
    Proxy->>GRPC: GRPCInferenceService.ModelInfer<br/>gRPC, Optional TLS
    GRPC-->>Proxy: ModelInferResponse<br/>gRPC protobuf
    Proxy->>Marshaler: Encode response to JSON<br/>In-process
    Marshaler-->>Proxy: JSON response body<br/>(multi-dim arrays, base64 bytes)
    Proxy-->>Client: HTTP 200 JSON Response<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS

    Note over Client,GRPC: Flow 2: Model Metadata Request

    Client->>Proxy: GET /v2/models/{name}<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS
    Proxy->>GRPC: GRPCInferenceService.ModelMetadata<br/>gRPC, Optional TLS
    GRPC-->>Proxy: ModelMetadataResponse<br/>gRPC protobuf
    Proxy-->>Client: HTTP 200 JSON Response<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS
